UserCode.UserInterfaces
Interface ILocation

All Known Implementing Classes:
DisplayObject
public interface ILocation

ILocation interface provides methods that allows the manipulation of an objects location. Can be used for an object in a 3D environment that utilizes the X,Y,Z axis.

Version:
14-02-2021, 0.1
Author:
Kristopher Randle
